Even the best applications in the world have bugs. It's normal, as sometimes the code can fail or you can simply forget to add a goddamned comma on the code and the app gets more errors than you can count.
In these cases, the users play an important role on BUG reporting. If bugs are reported, the app creators can easily track them down and fix 'em up. Thanks for your interest in keeping this app bug-free and safe :) Please use the button to open the BUG reporting form!
